r, direct, and culturally relevant. I\'ll translate the digital architecture to \"ARQUITETURA DIGITAL,\" and I will be working on a modern front-end description to \"Desenvolvimento de interfaces modernas refinadas com algoritmos gr\303\241ficos nativos, APIs eficientes e arquiteturas seguras em React.\" I also did the \"OPEN ACADEMIC PROJECT MATRIX\" translation to \"VER PROJETOS E PORTF\303\223LIO COMPLETO\".\n\n\n**Translating Strength Section**\n\nI am almost done translating Section 5 and I have finished translating Section 4! Now, I\'ve translated the \"Recorde Pessoal de Supino\", \"Consist\303\252ncia Di\303\241ria\", \"Treino Di\303\241rio / Foco Total\", and \"Piso de For\303\247a Elevado\" for Section 4\'s bench-pressing text, so this part of my portfolio is complete. I\'m focusing on \"Vamos Construir Algo Excecional\" for Section 5 now, so I have to translate \"Iniciar Conversa,\" \"Mensagem Direta no Instagram,\" and \"[ MOVIMENTA PARA MORFAR A MATRIZ DE VETORES ]\". I will then check `src/components/FarLeftSpine.tsx`.\n\n\n"
